title: S16 Ep76: Afterlife Insights into Suicide, Murder, Trauma w/ Siobhan Smith
itunes:title: Afterlife Insights into Suicide, Murder, Trauma w/ Siobhan Smith
description:
Darkness Radio presents Afterlife Insights into Suicide, Murder, Trauma with guest Siobhan Smith

Dave & Tim have a real, raw conversation about the Afterlife and communication with souls that have been lost to tragedy, trauma and suicide with guest Siobhan Smith. 

What really happens to us in those moments life ends and the afterlife begins. Siobhan shares her stories and experiences.

Follow Siobhan here: www.facebook.com/MEDIUMGSU

Instagram: @GrievingSoulsUnite
